{"tid":1465191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日之後會點？","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:55:01.000Z","uid":95173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1a81c5f7cccebed13c5a5bbfa8120f516e0a2dd4","tid":1465191,"uid":95173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:52:11.000Z","msg":"無人知 但我地嘅態度可以決定到結果<br />\n連登出嘅分化同割席post都係五毛出<br />\n我相信香港人 <br />\n我相信現場手足<br />\n我相信連登手足<br />\n大家早已對不分化不割席有共識<br />\n連出街啲阿伯都知咩叫各有各做be water<br />\n<br />\n<em>唔好再討論分化定割席</em><br />\n<br />\n我相信愛香港嘅你地<br />\n到今時今日都唔會割<br />\n已經冇得割 大家同一條船<br />\n唔需要求大家唔好分化或者唔好割席<br />\n因為我相信你地唔會<br />\n<br />\n宜家最需要係重整旗鼓<br />\n重新出發 停止失敗論<br />\n可以檢討同討論<br />\n唔需要再討論分化定割席依個問題<br />\n因為我地早有共識<br />\n<br />\n我相信香港人"},{"pid":"f466dd4779d6cd6b13695123f5b387a77d5510b8","tid":1465191,"uid":95173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:52:56.000Z","msg":"今日完咗<br />\n我唔知大家會唔會再出機場<br />\n但8.18 可以開始宣傳定"},{"pid":"8fc4916e2d1c83587af84bf9c765816d80c0efd0","tid":1465191,"uid":95173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:53:31.000Z","msg":"不受傷不被捕<br />\n少你一個好少<br />\n多你一個好多"},{"pid":"b38ac37f6469850c1aa5270cd05a84a0e2a1655c","tid":1465191,"uid":95173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:54:19.000Z","msg":"冇記錯仲有8.16 㩒錢大行動"},{"pid":"16c3fc3e1cac98d90a9feeca5a289caa79dc7b81","tid":1465191,"uid":95173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:54:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W0rgCmc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW0rgCmc.jpg&h=275ad972&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WYDe8sT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWYDe8sT.jpg&h=e8e79e09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad6bce2ea2f636f6602321321d9f506c71e59e1d","tid":1465191,"uid":95173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:55:01.000Z","msg":"香港 加